msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.97:0.2"
msgid "9. Gaṅgāpeyyālavagga "
msgstr "9. Abbreviated Texts on the Ganges "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.97:0.3"
msgid "97. Paṭhamasamuddaninnasutta "
msgstr "97. Slanting to the Ocean "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.97:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gaṅgā nadī samuddaninnā samuddapoṇā samuddapabbhārā; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the Ganges river slants, slopes, and inclines to the ocean. "

msgctxt "sn45.97:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant who develops the noble eightfold path slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.97:1.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn45.97:1.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn45.97:1.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.97:1.6"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
